y their \ldblquote enchant\rdblquote  abilities. They target the permanent or player they will enchant. (See rule 415.3.) An Aura permanent doesn\rquote t target anything.\par      Neither Equipment spells nor Equipment permanents are targeted. (See rule 415.3.) An Equipment may have abilities which are targeted.\par      A spell or ability on the stack can\rquote t target itself.\par      A spell that targets the same object or player more than once isn\rquote t a \ldblquote spell with a single target.\rdblquote \par \par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid215233 Team\par }\pard\plain \s27\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid215233 In a multiplayer game between teams, players win or lose as a group rather than as individuals.}{\insrsid215233\delrsid11615783  }{\insrsid215233 The Two-Headed Giant, Emperor, and Teams multiplayer variants all use teams.\par \par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid215233 Teammate\par }\pard\plain \s27\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid215233 In a multiplayer game between teams, a player\rquote s }{\insrsid215233\charrsid11615783 teammates}{\insrsid215233  are the other players on his or her team, and the player\rquote s opponents are all players not on his or her team.\par \par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f4\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid215233 Teams\par }\pard\plain \s27\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\